### Day 3a: Sessions, State & Context Compaction
- Built stateful agents using Sessions
- Used InMemorySessionService and DatabaseSessionService
- Persisted conversations across restarts using SQLite
- Implemented Context Compaction to summarize long conversations
- Managed structured session state using ToolContext

### Day 3b: Long-Term Memory
- Integrated MemoryService for cross-session recall
- Transferred session data into long-term memory
- Enabled memory retrieval using `load_memory` and `preload_memory`
- Implemented automatic memory saving using callbacks
- Demonstrated cross-session knowledge recall
- Understood memory consolidation for scalable systems
